snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP FIRED FROM FANTASTIC BEASTS FRANCHISE?! | Double Toasted
snippet.description:
JOHNNY DEPP FIRED FROM FANTASTIC BEASTS FRANCHISE?! | Double Toasted - The Johnny Depp Libel Trial reddit has been filled with people discussing how Depp loses his court case, as Fantastic Beasts has now asked him to resign. Why did Depp resign however? Because whether or not the allegations of abuse with Amber Heard is true, and with this news surrounding Depp no matter what he's attached to, Warner Bros. put their foot down and said enough' enough, with Depp's problems interfering with their money! We discuss this bit of news and whether or not we agree with the decisions made in this funny video!
